Igdtuw currently offers 5 Btech courses, one dual degree course (B.Tech+MBA),One course for B.Arch and One couse of BBA For undergraduates, 4 4 Mtech courses ,MCA, M.Plan and Mba couses for postgraduates, and 10 Ph.D courses.

University offers Btech in 5 streams 1. Computer science and artificial Intelligence(CSAI) 
 2. Computer science engineering (CSE) 
 3.Information Technology(IT) 
 4. Electronics and Communication(ECE)

University offers M.Tech. in 4 streams 1.CSE(Artificial Intelligence)
